## Part 3: Data Sufficiency for Presentation 🎯

This is the critical part. I checked whether your **demo data** (25 shipments + their scenarios) is sufficient to **demonstrate every feature** during your presentation.

### ✅ Features That Will Show Up Naturally

| Feature | Demo Data Coverage | Verdict |
|---------|-------------------|---------|
